### Today's 5 Problems - ALL SOLVED:
1. ✅ COMPLETED - Find Maximum Element (CUSTOM)
   Algorithm: Single pass traversal
   Complexity: O(n) time, O(1) space
   Status: SOLVED ✅
   
2. ✅ COMPLETED - Two Sum (LEETCODE #1)
   Algorithm: Brute force nested loops
   Complexity: O(n²) time, O(1) space
   Status: SOLVED ✅
   
3. ✅ COMPLETED - Find Sum of All Elements (CUSTOM)
   Algorithm: Accumulation through traversal
   Complexity: O(n) time, O(1) space
   Status: SOLVED ✅
   
4. ✅ COMPLETED - Valid Palindrome / Reverse Array (CUSTOM/LEETCODE)
   Algorithm: Two pointer from both ends
   Complexity: O(n) time, O(1) space
   Status: SOLVED ✅
   
5. ✅ COMPLETED - Best Time to Buy and Sell Stock (LEETCODE #121)
   Algorithm: Tracking minimum price and maximum profit
   Complexity: O(n) time, O(1) space
   Status: SOLVED ✅

## Key Learnings from Today's 5 Problems
- ✅ Index starts at 0, not 1
- ✅ Array access is O(1) due to contiguous memory
- ✅ Traversal is O(n) - must visit each element
- ✅ Two Sum uses nested loops - O(n²) brute force
- ✅ Can optimize by tracking minimum/maximum
- ✅ Palindrome check using two pointers: O(n) time, O(1) space
- ✅ Profit problem: track min price, calculate profit at each step
- ✅ Single pass solution often optimal for tracking problems

