## Concepts to Remember
- **Max/Min:** Keep track of one variable, update as you traverse
- **Sum:** Initialize to 0, accumulate as you go
- **Palindrome:** Use two pointers from both ends, check equality
- **Profit Tracking:** Find minimum before current, calculate profit
- **Two Sum:** Can brute force with O(n²) or optimize with hash map later

